  "title": "Part-time Bar Back & Server",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Vatos</strong></p><p>Vatos is known for bold Korean-Mexican flavours and an exciting bar program focused on great cocktails, tequila, and energetic service. We value teamwork, learning, and a positive, fast-paced environment.</p><p><strong>The Role</strong></p><p>We’re looking for a Part-Time Bar Back / Server who loves the bar scene and is eager to learn. This role is ideal for someone interested in bartending who wants hands-on experience in a busy, supportive bar team.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>•\tSupport bartenders by keeping the bar stocked, organised, and service-ready<br />•\tAssist with glassware, ice, garnishes, and bar setup and cleanup<br />•\tServe guests with friendly, attentive service<br />•\tTake food and drink orders accurately<br />•\tMaintain cleanliness and hygiene standards<br />•\tWork closely with the bar and service team during busy shifts</p><p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><p>•\tInterest in bartending and bar culture<br />•\tPositive attitude and willingness to learn<br />•\tTeam player who works well under pressure<br />•\tAvailability for both lunch and dinner shifts</p><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><p>•\tLearn from an experienced team and exciting bar program<br />•\tGain hands-on bar and service experience<br />•\tStaff meals, uniform, and staff discounts<br />•\tOpportunity to grow within the team</p>",
